  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want a standard way to update my desktop app version on MacOS.\r\n\r\n### Description & current behavior\r\n**Type**: Fix\r\n\r\n**Current implementation**\r\n<img width=\"342\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-10-24 a la s 1 00 32 p m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/47439653-0d76be80-d7ad-11e8-9269-fbb099f8e59e.png\">\r\n\r\nThe current implementation for upgrading to the latest version has the following issues:\r\n\r\n- By being a primary button, it compites with the main action under Profile that is to share your contact.\r\n- Once we add more options under Profile, the button will get lost.\r\n- It is not a standard way to update a MacOS app. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe update experience should follow [this definition](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/5812).\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Profile\r\n\r\n### Note\r\nTBD how to do it on Windows and Linux\r\n",
